{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, the transmitted beampattern should form a null space towards the potential eavesdropper or the clutter point to improve the performance.",
    "Consequently, beamforming design, which can form the directional beam with high radiation power, is an important technique to achieve this goal.",
    "Qi et al. [111] minimized the beampattern mismatch subject to the QoS constraint via optimizing the transmit beamforming vectors at the ISAC-BS.",
    "The sensing SINR was maximized by Wang et al. [113] while satisfying the QoS and transmit power constraints.",
    "For the networked ISAC system, Cheng et al. [117] investigated the coordinated beamforming design for the performance improvement."
  ]
}